      "unit_type": "paragraph",
      "unit_order": 1,
      "unit_order_status": "known",
      "source_text": "When DMM is used for clinical or nonclinical studies in addition to typical liquid approaches (e.g., liquid plasma samples) in the same studies, these two methods should be cross validated as described (Refer to Section 6.2). For nonclinical TK studies, refer to Section 4.1 of ICH S3A Q&A. Feedback from the appropriate regulatory authorities is encouraged in early drug development.",
